            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
                </ab>
                <p>
                    matirai koṇṭa kō-p-parakē<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ri-paṉmaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="37">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num> Āvatu
                </p>
                <p>
                    Eyiṟ-kōṭṭattu Eyil-nāṭṭu-k ka
                    <lb n="2"/>ṇṇa-maṅkalattu Ūrōm Ivv-ūr muṭittalai kiḻavaṉ māṇikka <hi rend="grantha">śa<unclear>r</unclear>mma</hi>ṉum Attaṇaṅ kiḻavaṉ kanaka<!--check: more letters on photo: kiḻavaṉ kaṅ * * kha *-->
                    <lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">śa<unclear>r</unclear>mma</hi>ṉum muṭittalai kiḻavaṉ paṭṭa-<hi rend="grantha">śa<unclear>r</unclear>mma</hi>
                    <lb n="4"/>ṉum Ik-kuṭi-t tirumalaṅ kiḻavaṉ nārāya
                    <lb n="5"/>ṇa-<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi>ṭṭaṉum Ik-kuṭi-k kampa-<hi rend="grantha">śarmma</hi>ṉum Ik-kuṭi nārā
                    <lb n="6"/>yaṇa-<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi>ṭṭaṉum vaya <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ḻāṉ Aṅkāṭi <hi rend="grantha">śarmma</hi>ṉum kaḷattu
                    <lb n="7"/>ḻāṉ nīla kaṇ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> m Ivvaṉaivōm Eṅkaḷ pūmi-y-āṉa kaṇṇa-maṅ
                    
                    <lb n="8"/>kalam nila-vilai-y-āvaṇa-k kaiyeḻuttu kacci-p-pēṭṭu-t tiru-vekkā va
                    <lb n="9"/>ṇai-k kiṭant-aruḷiṉa Aṉanta-nārāyaṇa-parama-svāmikku viṟṟu-k kuṭukkiṟa nilam kīḻpāṟ
                    <lb n="10"/>k’ ellai tiru vattiyūr Ellaikku mēṟku vekkā vāṟu tuṭaṅki vaṭakku nōkki-p pōki
                    <lb n="11"/>ṟa vatikku mēṟkum teṉpāṟk’ ellai vekkā vāṟṟukku vaṭakkum mēlpāṟk’ el
                    <lb n="12"/>lai pattaṉap pāṭi Ellaikku kiḻakkum vaṭapāṟk’ ellai karum puḻāṉ viḷākattu
                    <lb n="13"/>muṭittalai kiḻavaṉ Uṭaiya paḷḷi-p paṭṭi-y nīr pāyuṅ kālukku-t teṟku tiruvattiyū
                    <lb n="14"/>r Ellaiyuḷ Eṅkaḷ kaṇṇa-maṅkalat tētta māṉa kīḻai Araiyum mēlaiyaraiyum
                    <lb n="15"/>Uṭpaṭṭa Iṉ-ṉāṟ-pāṟk’ ellai yuḷḷum Uḷ nilam oḻiv’ iṉṟi Oṭump’ ōṭi Āmai nakuntatum kuḷamum koṭṭa
                    <lb n="16"/>kāramum nīr-nilamum kollaiyum maṉaiyum maṉai-p paṭappaiyum kaṉṟu-mēy-kaḻaniyum nīr pōṉa vā
                    <lb n="17"/>ykkālum mēṉōkkiya maramum kīṇōkkiya kiṇaṟu mīṉpaṭu paḷḷamum tēṉ paṭu pottamu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kā
                    <lb n="18"/>ṭum Uṭpaṭa Eppērpaṭṭa nilam Uḷ nilam Oḻiv’iṉṟi viṟṟu Emmil icainta poṉ kācu kalaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="19"/>muṉṉūṟṟ’ aṟupat keḻu kaḻañcum kiḻi yaṟa-k kai-k-koṇṭu tiru-vekkā vaṇaik kiṭant-aruḷiṉa Aṉanta-nārā
                    <lb n="20"/>yaṇa-p-parama-svāmikku viṟṟu-k kuṭuttōm kaṇṇa-maṅkalattu Ūravarōm Eṅkaḷ karumpuḻāṉ vi
                    <lb n="21"/>ḷākattukku nīr pānta kāl kaṇṇa maṅkalattukku mēl nīr muṟaimai y-āvat’ āka Ip-pari coṭṭi Emmil icai
                    <lb n="22"/>nta poruḷ <num value="367">3 100+ 6 10+ 7</num> kaḻañcum kai-k-koṇṭu tiru-vekkā vaṇaik kiṭant-aruḷiṉa Aṉanta<surplus>nta</surplus>-nārāyaṇa-parama
                    <lb n="23"/><hi rend="grantha">svāmi</hi>kku viṟṟu-k kuṭuttōm kaṇṇa-maṅkalatt’ ūrōm Ituvē poruḷ māvaṟuti-p poruṭ celav-ōlai y-ā
                    <lb n="24" break="no"/>vat’ ākavum Iru-kāl-āvatu mu-k-kāl-āvatum Emmil icainta poṉ ki<seg rend="check">ḻi</seg> maṟak kai-k-koṇṭu tiru-vekkā vaṇai
                    <lb n="25"/>-k kiṭant-aruḷiṉa parama-svāmikku viṟṟu-k kuṭuttōm kaṇṇa-maṅkalattu Ūrōm Ivarkaḷ paṇiyāl nila
                    <lb n="26"/>vilai-y-āvaṇam Eḻutiṉēṉ kaṇṇa-maṅkalam-uṭaiyāṉ Aruḷāḷaṉ pērāyiramuṭaiyāṉēṉ Ivai
                    <lb n="27"/>Eṉ Eḻuttu <g type="pc">.</g>
                </p>
